<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 24 at 6:58AM EST  by NWS Buffalo</headline>
<description>...AREAS OF FOG THIS MORNING...
Areas of fog will continue this morning across much of Erie and
Niagara counties, including the Buffalo Metro area and Niagara
Falls. Visibility will be reduced to less than a half mile at
times. Motorists should use caution and allow a little extra time
to reach your destination.</description>
